title: Highway to Heaven - S01E13 - Another Song for Christmas
description:
13. Another Song for Christmas   
Community Score
8.5 Great 	1
review
First aired: 12/19/1984

In this variation on "A Christmas Carol," Jonathan and Mark have a Dickens of a time--literally--bringing Holiday joy 
into the heart of "Honest Eddie": a crooked-as-they-come used-car dealer.

Writer: Dan Gordon
Director: Michael Landon
Guest star: Matt Shakman (Bobby Ratchett), Jeff Doucette (Dave Ratchett), Paul Barselou (Jeff), Charles Tyner 
(Caleb Fish), Valorie Grear (Beth Ratchett), Kathryn Fuller (Bonnie), Bill Shick (Tony), Herta Ware (Grandma), 
Casey Erickson (Helper), Ivor Barry (Joseph), Bill Quinn (I) (Millard Watkins), Kellie Martin (Lisa Ratchett), 
Virginia Keehnne (Sarah Ratchett), William Utay (Worker # 2), Hap Lawrence (Worker #1), Don Beddoe (Kris), 
Daniel Brown (Eddy at age 8), Geoffrey Lewis ("Honest" Eddie)
